# CI/CD Pipeline Template

## Purpose
Generate comprehensive CI/CD pipelines for various platforms.

## Template Variables
- {{project_name}}: Project name
- {{language}}: Programming language
- {{platform}}: CI platform (github, gitlab, circleci)
- {{tests}}: Test types to run
- {{build_steps}}: Build commands
- {{deploy_targets}}: Deployment targets
- {{branches}}: Protected branches

## GitHub Actions Example

